{"tid":1159950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘道政府合署 發現兩米長大蛇","createTime":"2019-05-18T06:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T14:42:29.000Z","uid":62257,"like":268,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"0e37e2a904f7e1333e6b1d72d0702ca755f57ddc","tid":1159950,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190518/59614134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190518%2F59614134&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=c23b6e84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190518%2F59614134&h=39e8e390\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190518/59614134</a><br />\n早上8時許，金鐘道政府合署低座3樓，保安員發現一條約兩米長的蛇縮在廁所一角，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n3樓是生死登記及婚姻登記處，警方到場時該條蛇已爬到廁所門外，一動不動，於是用圍板圍住牠。稍後「蛇王林」到場，手到拿來將小蛇捉走。據「蛇王林」稱，這是水律蛇，無毒，事件沒有影響登記處的服務。"},{"pid":"403195b21f81cb618b6a04f08be7a1f196106192","tid":1159950,"uid":192190,"like":909,"dislike":5,"score":904,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:08:42.000Z","msg":"政府<br />\n蛇王<br />\nMATCH"},{"pid":"a20fd2c7b32980914945cdd19cda9c9bcbc404a9","tid":1159950,"uid":27664,"like":96,"dislike":3,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"好爆喎，點會有蛇架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8955b20a951a734a8a6cfec36c0ec2167d99949","tid":1159950,"uid":86723,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"未見過大蛇痾尿?"},{"pid":"fa4092e4eb0859df110778614ad51da26ec71f6e","tid":1159950,"uid":25900,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"周鳩圍都係蛇<br />\n走野又蛇"},{"pid":"474a6d458073ef8d9ec0be372a75b3581a3680c6","tid":1159950,"uid":156144,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime